{
  "stem": "19441.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 93.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I had friends and going to the picture theater.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was altogether blind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother, the oldest, was in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The middle one was like as a soldier in uniform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later, the last few weeks, they didn't-- they took away their military uniform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they just gave them-- I don't remember-- blue or green uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they send them to a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were there some.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it still wasn't visible how dangerous it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the-- in the last few days, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a man who was a, a conductor on the train, conductor, he told somebody that he went with the train.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he heard that they are taking people to the concentration camp and what going what's happening there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said that to his girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And straight away, he took her away from the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she survived without going to the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- when I heard that people are hiding and people are going to Hungary in the last few weeks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was what period of time?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Can you remember the date?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It must have be in January, '42.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't know why I didn't-- I didn't like to hide.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't like to go to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because then when we heard something that it was to go to [INAUDIBLE] factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said, why should I hide?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Is that so bad?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we will work in [INAUDIBLE] factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the brother, when they started to hear something, so they went to the woods to fight with the partisans because fight against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they didn't know about that they will take us away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
